{"tid":767544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟要點應付d厚面皮既人","createTime":"2018-08-04T15:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T15:48:20.000Z","uid":12724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a420f4e99f0f6a1d85235cdd9632abd1cd0372ee","tid":767544,"uid":12724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"有個舊同事，30歲到啦，話屋企人幫佢搵相體對象，搵左個40歲到既女人，話住加拿大，個舊同事見到未見過個女人就話要辭職再同現任個女朋友分手去食軟飯，但係佢無論係樣身高性格才華都無樣得，過一排佢又話唔去加拿大啦人地派左好人卡比佢收左佢皮，但佢似乎完全唔知個問題係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話自己錯過左段良緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二個極品係個已經無聯絡既男仔朋友，有幾次同佢出街，佢次次都要搭的士，落車個陣無比錢就走左去，咁我見幾廿蚊就算啦，到左食飯，食完佢就拎起張單去櫃台啦，個陣仲諗可能佢覺得樣樣都aa咁計錢好樣衰就一人比一次，點撚知佢出去櫃台放底張單就望住我笑笑口，之後話出去等我，我屌自此之後佢約親我食飯都無理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多哩d奇怪人諗起再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30a88d09668b0559691b8f8e6550ca6d7a8c3e0","tid":767544,"uid":12724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c3b5291bc28e3f20011845b06ffb9aaf803126","tid":767544,"uid":82482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"求包養<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5a68bd5d899b2fc8339dafc416dfb18d4b0fcd","tid":767544,"uid":183515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"食飯唔俾錢真係好賤，如果唔使俾面佢，下次直接同收銀講分開收，然後俾自己果份"},{"pid":"e97332ffbe99afff042ffab05e413b9824f482dc","tid":767544,"uid":174641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"咁你點解要幫佢俾埋？"},{"pid":"918afa36163740e3e257bd4245ea68385e9d8f59","tid":7